Class MarkingNetGenerator

  • java.lang.Object

    public class MarkingNetGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<PetriNet>
    Given a Petri net, generate other nets with all possible initial markings up to a given limit m.

        public MarkingNetGenerator(PetriNet pn,
                           int tokenLimit,
                           boolean addToInitialMarking)
        Create a new MarkingNetGenerator instance for the given arguments.
        Parameters:
        pn - The Petri net for which all initial markings are generated.
        tokenLimit - The limit for the number of token on the net.
        addToInitialMarking - if true, the initial marking of the Petri nets is only increased; otherwise the initial marking is ignored and overwritten.

      • MarkingNetGenerator

        public MarkingNetGenerator(PetriNet pn,
                           int tokenLimit,
                           boolean addToInitialMarking,
                           java.util.Collection<java.util.Set<Place>> requiredPlaces)
        Create a new MarkingNetGenerator instance for the given arguments.
        Parameters:
        pn - The Petri net for which all initial markings are generated.
        tokenLimit - The limit for the number of token on the net.
        addToInitialMarking - if true, the initial marking of the Petri nets is only increased; otherwise the initial marking is ignored and overwritten.
        requiredPlaces - a collection of places which must get at least one token. For each element, all markings which do not put at least one token on this nodes are ignored.

      • getMarkedNet

        private PetriNet getMarkedNet(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> marking)
        Create a fresh copy of our Petri net. This function deep-copies the Petri Net that was given to this class' constructor. Then the initial marking of this new Petri net is set to the specified marking.
        Parameters:
        marking - The initial marking for the fresh clone of the Petri net
        Returns:
        A fresh clone of this class' Petri net with the given marking
